<h1 id="5-bmon">5. <a href="https://github.com/tgraf/bmon">bmon</a></h1>
<p>Bmon (Bandwidth Monitor) is a tool similar to nload that shows the traffic load on all network interfaces in the system. The output also consists of a graph and a section with details at the package level.</p>

