<h1 id="10-cbm---color-bandwidth-meter">10. <a href="https://github.com/resurrecting-open-source-projects/cbm">cbm - Color bandwidth meter</a></h1>
<p>A small, simple bandwidth monitor that displays the volume of traffic through network interfaces. There are no more options, only traffic statistics are displayed and updated in real time.</p>

<p>Installation example on a Linux distro:</p>

