<h1 id="14-trafshow">14. <a href="https://github.com/mattetambu/Trafshow">Trafshow</a></h1>
<p>Like netwatch and pktstat, trafshow reports the current active connections, their protocol and the data transfer speed for each connection. It can filter connections using pcap filters. Monitor only tcp connections.</p>

