<h1 id="17-dstat">17. <a href="http://dag.wiee.rs/home-made/dstat/">dstat</a></h1>
<p>Dstat is a versatile tool (written in python) that can monitor different system statistics and report them in a batch mode or record the data in a csv or similar file. This example shows how to use dstat to report network bandwidth.</p>

